OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold start with some frost,
OL,6,Fand variable cloud in the east.
OL,7,FOtherwise a dry day with increasingly
OL,8,Fsunny spells, but feeling a bit cooler
OL,9,Fthan recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry throughout
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight. Clear skies
OL,13,Fat first, but high cloud spreading in
OL,14,Ffrom the west later. Chance of some
OL,15,Fpatchy overnight frost developing
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
