OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAfter a chilly start it will
OL,6,Fbe another dry and bright day and
OL,7,Ffeeling a bit milder again. Sunshine
OL,8,Fquite hazy in the west, good sunny
OL,9,Fspells in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,12,Fcloud and bright spells on Sunday and
OL,13,FMonday, often dry but with the
OL,14,Foccasional spell of rain. Becoming
OL,15,Fwindier Tuesday as rain spreads east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
